properties.headline: FLOODING - THE UNINCORPORATED AREA OF THE WESTERN REGION various roads
properties.otherAdvice:
The following roads are closed  due to flooding:

The Cut Line (Tibooburra to Borrona Downs);

The Cut Line (Borrona Downs to Wanaaring); and

Mutawintji Road (Mutawintji NP to White Cliffs).

In addition 4WDs only (no trailers or caravans) are allowed on Silver City Hwy between Packsaddle and Tibooburra.

A number of local roads are also closed. Further information can be obtained from 08 8082 6660.
